00:46:45,400 --> 00:46:49,440
One more chance.
Will you leave or not?

780
00:46:49,720 --> 00:46:53,280
I will not leave.

781
00:47:05,840 --> 00:47:06,840
What just happened?

782
00:47:08,240 --> 00:47:12,360
Are we all back in our own bodies? Yay!

783
00:47:12,360 --> 00:47:15,640
Wow, the ghost here left pretty quickly.

784
00:47:15,640 --> 00:47:18,800
And that ghost wanted so many benefits.

785
00:47:19,840 --> 00:47:21,840
Wait, what do you mean by that?

786
00:47:22,560 --> 00:47:26,040
I don’t get it.
I just blacked out and woke up again.

787
00:47:26,040 --> 00:47:30,040
It doesn’t make sense.
Don’t be so superstitious. Just sit down.

788
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:34,280
Uh, are we all clear now?

789
00:47:34,680 --> 00:47:38,120
If so, can I just ask something?

790
00:47:38,120 --> 00:47:42,640
What’s the name of this company again?
I didn’t quite catch it.

791
00:47:45,080 --> 00:47:47,200
Glamorous Airline.

792
00:47:47,920 --> 00:47:48,920
Oh.

793
00:47:54,240 --> 00:47:56,240
Well then, goodbye.

794
00:47:57,280 --> 00:47:59,760
Hey, where are you going?
You’re not waiting for the HR interview?

795
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:01,920
I don’t think there will be an interview.

796
00:48:01,920 --> 00:48:02,880
Why not?

797
00:48:02,880 --> 00:48:06,920
Because the office I came for is Pegasus Airline.

798
00:48:10,200 --> 00:48:11,600
Goodbye.

799
00:48:12,520 --> 00:48:13,520
Oh no!

800
00:48:14,800 --> 00:48:18,120
A swivel chair.
Nampetch is scared of wheels!

801
00:48:18,120 --> 00:48:20,920
Wheels.
Nampetch is scared.

802
00:48:20,920 --> 00:48:22,000
Hey, let me ask you something.

803
00:48:22,000 --> 00:48:24,000
How many things have you been scared of since you left your house?

804
00:48:24,200 --> 00:48:25,360
Shouldn’t your name be Miss Fear instead?

805
00:48:26,200 --> 00:48:27,720
You're scared all the way...

806
00:48:28,200 --> 00:48:29,200
I'm Miss Fear.

807
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:31,000
You’ve been screaming all day.

808
00:48:32,600 --> 00:48:34,600
How have you even survived this long?

809
00:48:36,360 --> 00:48:37,640
I'm scared of water bowls.

810
00:48:37,640 --> 00:48:38,880
Are you scared of holy water too?

811
00:48:39,120 --> 00:48:41,360
Stop it. It's Chaba here.

812
00:48:41,360 --> 00:48:42,600
Don’t do this to me!

813
00:48:43,800 --> 00:48:45,160
Let's sit down.

814
00:48:47,840 --> 00:48:50,520
Whoa...body swaps…

815
00:48:50,520 --> 00:48:52,160
and Nampetch…

816
00:48:52,160 --> 00:48:54,160
only at Glamorous Airline.

817
00:48:55,280 --> 00:48:56,680
So true.

818
00:48:59,560 --> 00:49:01,560
it got my finger and now I’ve got rust.

819
00:49:01,560 --> 00:49:04,320
It's rusty! Will I get tetanus?

820
00:49:09,200 --> 00:49:11,480
You must be Kreetha, right?

821
00:49:12,200 --> 00:49:14,760
And you must be All-New.

822
00:49:14,960 --> 00:49:16,440
I'm sorry.

823
00:49:16,680 --> 00:49:19,440
Wait, my shades hit his face earlier!

824
00:49:20,320 --> 00:49:21,320
I'm sorry.

825
00:49:22,520 --> 00:49:26,200
Then let's start with checking the passengers' tickets.

826
00:49:26,200 --> 00:49:27,000
Alright.

827
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:28,000
It's called boarding passes.

828
00:49:28,240 --> 00:49:30,120
Oh, right.

829
00:49:32,040 --> 00:49:34,720
Hello, A rider is here for delivery.

830
00:49:37,720 --> 00:49:38,720
How could we receive a rider?
Who ordered a rider?

831
00:49:40,480 --> 00:49:42,320
How did you end up in my body, Tid-Gift?

832
00:49:42,960 --> 00:49:43,440
Cut!

833
00:49:43,840 --> 00:49:45,240
How did you end up in my body, Tid-Gift?

834
00:49:45,920 --> 00:49:46,920
Oh, it's Chai.

835
00:49:48,280 --> 00:49:49,280
Wait, I'm confused.

836
00:49:49,360 --> 00:49:50,360
Yes, it's really confusing.

837
00:49:50,960 --> 00:49:53,760
Wow, it's so clean.

838
00:49:53,760 --> 00:49:55,160
Wait, wait, wait.

839
00:49:55,160 --> 00:49:56,800
We haven't called you yet.

840
00:49:59,680 --> 00:50:01,680
Sorry, I dropped my money.

841
00:50:02,320 --> 00:50:05,040
Are you alright? You look like someone
who's just finished scrubbing the toilets...

842
00:50:05,040 --> 00:50:07,040
Nicole!

843
00:50:07,280 --> 00:50:08,280
Coco!

844
00:50:12,280 --> 00:50:14,080
Your face looks like a toilet scrubber is better.

845
00:50:14,280 --> 00:50:15,600
Your face looks like a toilet scrubber.

846
00:50:16,680 --> 00:50:18,080
Chaba.

847
00:50:18,560 --> 00:50:19,960
Chaba!

848
00:50:22,120 --> 00:50:23,360
The one who gets to smile is me!

849
00:50:24,080 --> 00:50:27,080
Chaba is possessed. Alright, Tid-Gift?

850
00:50:27,520 --> 00:50:28,520
Tid-Gift!

851
00:50:30,360 --> 00:50:32,760
She's possessed now.

852
00:50:33,600 --> 00:50:34,600
Chaba is possessed!

853
00:50:35,000 --> 00:50:36,080
When the hell did the ghost get inside her?

854
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:40,320
An owl ghost.

855
00:50:40,440 --> 00:50:41,440
That's an owl ghost.

856
00:50:44,040 --> 00:50:45,280
That's a chicken ghost.

857
00:50:45,280 --> 00:50:46,560
That must be a chicken for sure.

858
00:50:50,200 --> 00:50:51,200
That's Moo-deng.

859
00:50:51,880 --> 00:50:53,120
That's a Moo-deng ghost.

860
00:50:58,760 --> 00:50:59,960
Hold it!

861
00:51:00,720 --> 00:51:03,440
She wasn't even looking but that got her! Moo-deng!

862
00:51:04,080 --> 00:51:05,680
Who gets the white envelopes...

863
00:51:05,680 --> 00:51:08,080
will be in the new Glamorous Airline's commercial.

864
00:51:11,800 --> 00:51:12,800
Who’s the teacher?

865
00:51:14,000 --> 00:51:17,240
This is Ms. Dina and Ms. Piangduan,
who will be leading the workshop today.

866
00:51:17,240 --> 00:51:18,360
Aren’t they enemies?

867
00:51:18,360 --> 00:51:20,840
I didn’t outshine you, did I, Dina?

868
00:51:20,840 --> 00:51:22,840
Choose. Me or her?

869
00:51:23,680 --> 00:51:27,480
Someone put glass shards in my shoes.

870
00:51:28,200 --> 00:51:29,880
You think I don’t know it was you?

871
00:51:29,880 --> 00:51:32,120
Yes. I hate you.
